{"tid":1508403,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"下次記住每個人都要自備波子！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-08-26T13:47:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-30T05:41:32.000Z","uid":257834,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"80f73c4cf94ca1984566c766e9cfdf2fda8b79c2","tid":1508403,"uid":257834,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13:47:16.000Z","msg":"以琴日楊屋道為例<br />\n大家有共識係遠攻 但因為雙方距離太遠<br />\n除咗魔法 基本上扔磚大部分都扔唔中 對佢地係0攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyosYdh.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyosYdh.jpg&h=e19aff45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n除非大家有共識上前近攻 <br />\n否則如果大家要扔野嘅話 點解唔扔波子？<br />\n重溫一下琴日死嘅原因<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/fq3iq\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ffq3iq&d=qutgakuQBXsObMwiKtfrsYeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=1671ba73\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/fq3iq</a><br />\n諗下如果成地波子嘅話 我唔信佢哋可以咁順利咁快衝到上嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且波子棋真係好撚平 廿幾蚊一盒60粒波子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果每個手足扔一札十粒嘅話 唔知會有咩後果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一開頭扔黎做防線又得 啲狗沖埋黎個陣扔又得<br />\n記住唔好teamkill自己友就得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n希望每個人都可以自備波子<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">企後排嘅手足 希望你哋可以企前少少先扔 或者確定自己夠大力扔出去先好扔 我琴日已經俾你地噴到成身洗潔精啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"d10d293533c179ffe3231125d973442825203dfc","tid":1508403,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-26T13: